Merge branch 'master' of https://github.com/rolsanmordua-utexas/hackUTD.git

Merging all the things!!!!!!
Trying to save data through different activities

Addition of AutoCompleteParser in Java

Program takes objects from object recognition and searches for terms. Returns "Sugggestions" based on Google AutoComplete.

parsing country-to-language data

Creates a hashmap where the keys are names of countries, and values are ranked lists of which languages are most spoken in that country. Languages are only added to the list if they are supported by Google Translate. Data was formatted inconsistently, so it's parsed using regex.
